libegl1-mesa (2:1.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * This is actually libsunxi-mali-x11 disguised as libegl1-mesa. This is a
    hack to resolve a conflict with libegl1-mesa that also contains
    /usr/lib/arm-linux-gnueabihf/libEGL.so.

